# Find CEGUI includes and library
#
# This module defines
#  CEGUI_INCLUDE_DIR
#  CEGUI_LIBRARIES, the libraries to link against to use OGRE.
#  CEGUI_LIB_DIR, the location of the libraries
#  CEGUI_FOUND, If false, do not try to use OGRE
#
